  "text": "For the study of cancer, the application of these sensors is in finding better chemotherapy treatments. SECM has been shown to be capable of quantifying the effectiveness of anti-cancer drugs on specific types of cancer cells by monitoring the effect of the drug in real-time, and this type of system can be used to evaluate new drugs for treatment of specific forms of cancer [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . Quantification of the effect of anti-cancer drugs can lead to more effective chemotherapy that is less damaging on the patient, leading to a faster recovery and shorter hospital time.",
